    "is_elective": false,
    "description": "This course, ELECTRONICS II (ANALOGUE), builds upon foundational electronics principles, delving into amplifier design, oscillators, and switching circuits. It also introduces digital building blocks like flip-flops, counters, and registers, alongside an exploration of sequential logic design.",
    "outline": [
      {
